data.description: Magic on Malone Island. Besides being right on the lake with south facing views of the state park this island has gas, water and sewer!! Three bedrooms plus an office/den. Large open kitchen. All closets are walk in. Primary bedroom has lake views and an ensuite with soaking tub and shower. Roof replaced in 2022. Need more space? The three car garage has a walk in full attic ready to finish for more guests! Mille Lacs is a trophy lake known for muskies, bass and walleye. New hospital/clinic 10 min drive away. 125' of lake shore and roll in dock.
